msgid ""
"Understand Ray Data autoscaling and safely change a running Klein "
"streaming operator's parallelism."
msgstr "了解 Ray Data 自动伸缩，并安全调整运行中 Klein 流式算子的并行度。"

msgid "Autoscaling and live operator rescaling"
msgstr "自动伸缩与在线算子扩缩容"

msgid ""
"Scaling has three independent layers in Klein. Choose the layer that "
"matches the execution mode and the resource you need to change:"
msgstr "Klein 中的伸缩分为三个独立层级。请选择与执行模式及待调整资源相匹配的层级："

msgid "Layer"
msgstr "层级"

msgid "Execution mode"
msgstr "执行模式"

msgid "Decision owner"
msgstr "决策方"

msgid "Klein entry point"
msgstr "Klein 入口"

msgid "Ray Data worker pool"
msgstr "Ray Data worker 池"

msgid "Batch"
msgstr "批处理"

msgid "Ray Data"
msgstr "Ray Data"

msgid "`concurrency=(min, max)` on a callable-class transform"
msgstr "可调用类转换上的 `concurrency=(min, max)`"

msgid "Klein operator parallelism"
msgstr "Klein 算子并行度"

msgid "Streaming"
msgstr "流处理"

msgid "User, Dashboard, or external controller"
msgstr "用户、Dashboard 或外部控制器"

msgid "`rescale_operator()`"
msgstr "`rescale_operator()`"

msgid "Ray cluster nodes"
msgstr "Ray 集群节点"

msgid "Batch and streaming"
msgstr "批处理和流处理"

msgid "Ray cluster autoscaler"
msgstr "Ray 集群自动伸缩器"

msgid "Ray cluster configuration"
msgstr "Ray 集群配置"

msgid ""
"Klein does not currently include a metric-driven controller that "
"automatically changes streaming parallelism. The Dashboard and "
"`rescale_operator()` perform an explicit, live change to one operator. "
"The Dashboard submits the change asynchronously; the Python function "
"waits for its topology result. Ray's cluster autoscaler can provide nodes"
" for that request, but it does not choose the operator's parallelism."
msgstr ""
"Klein 目前不包含根据指标自动调整流式并行度的控制器。Dashboard 和 `rescale_operator()` "
"会对一个算子执行显式的在线变更。Dashboard 会异步提交变更；Python 函数则等待拓扑结果。Ray "
"集群自动伸缩器可为该请求提供节点，但不会替算子选择并行度。"

msgid ""
"`DataStream.rescale()` is a partitioning method. It limits which "
"downstream subtasks each upstream subtask can address; it does not add or"
" remove actors."
msgstr "`DataStream.rescale()` 是一种分区方法。它限制每个上游子任务可寻址的下游子任务，但不会添加或移除 actor。"

msgid "Autoscale a bounded transform"
msgstr "自动伸缩有界转换"

msgid ""
"In batch mode, Klein lowers compatible transforms to Ray Data and "
"forwards their concurrency setting. A callable class uses Ray actors, so "
"a `(min, max)` range gives Ray Data an autoscaling actor pool:"
msgstr ""
"在批处理模式下，Klein 将兼容转换下沉为 Ray Data，并转发其并发设置。可调用类使用 Ray actor，因此 `(min, max)`"
" 范围会为 Ray Data 提供自动伸缩 actor 池："

msgid ""
"Ray Data owns the utilization policy and the actor lifecycle. The range "
"limits workers, not cluster nodes, and each live worker requests the "
"transform's `num_cpus` and `num_gpus`. See Ray Data's [transform "
"concurrency guide](https://docs.ray.io/en/latest/data/transforming-"
"data.html#specifying-concurrency) for the policy in the installed Ray "
"version."
msgstr ""
"Ray Data 负责利用率策略和 actor 生命周期。该范围限制的是 worker 而非集群节点，每个活动 worker 都会请求转换的 "
"`num_cpus` 和 `num_gpus`。有关已安装 Ray 版本中的策略，请参阅 Ray Data "
"的[转换并发指南](https://docs.ray.io/en/latest/data/transforming-data.html"
"#specifying-concurrency)。"

msgid ""
"The same tuple has different behavior in Klein's native streaming "
"runtime: `(2, 8)` starts the operator at the lower bound, `2`. It neither"
" triggers a streaming policy nor caps a later `rescale_operator(..., "
"parallelism=...)` request. Set explicit policy bounds in an external "
"controller if one is required."
msgstr ""
"相同元组在 Klein 原生流式运行时中的行为不同：`(2, 8)` 会以其下限 `2` 启动算子。它既不会触发流式策略，也不会限制后续 "
"`rescale_operator(..., parallelism=...)` 请求。如需策略边界，请在外部控制器中显式设置。"

msgid "Prepare a streaming job for live rescaling"
msgstr "为流式作业准备在线扩缩容"

msgid ""
"Live rescaling changes one running operator without restarting the entire"
" job. The request is accepted only when all of these conditions hold:"
msgstr "在线扩缩容可在不重启整个作业的情况下更改一个运行中的算子。只有满足以下全部条件时，请求才会被接受："

msgid "Requirement"
msgstr "要求"

msgid "Current behavior"
msgstr "当前行为"

msgid "Job health"
msgstr "作业健康状态"

msgid "The job and every task instance must be `RUNNING`."
msgstr "作业和每个任务实例都必须处于 `RUNNING` 状态。"

msgid "Source topology"
msgstr "源拓扑"

msgid ""
"Multiple source operators and source subtasks are coordinated within "
"checkpoint domains."
msgstr "多个源算子和源子任务会在各自的检查点域内协调。"

msgid "Target"
msgstr "目标"

msgid ""
"Source, transactional-sink, and collecting-sink operators are not "
"supported."
msgstr "不支持源算子、事务型 sink 算子和收集型 sink 算子。"

msgid "Managed state"
msgstr "托管状态"

msgid "Target parallelism cannot exceed `state.keyed.max-parallelism`."
msgstr "目标并行度不能超过 `state.keyed.max-parallelism`。"

msgid "Coordination"
msgstr "协调"

msgid ""
"Only one rescale runs at a time; wait for its stabilization checkpoint "
"before the next one."
msgstr "一次只能运行一个扩缩容操作；请等待其稳定化检查点完成后再执行下一次操作。"

msgid "Capacity"
msgstr "容量"

msgid "Scale-out needs schedulable resources for the added subtasks."
msgstr "扩容需要为新增子任务提供可调度资源。"

msgid ""
"Set `state.keyed.max-parallelism` before the first checkpoint and keep it"
" stable:"
msgstr "请在第一个检查点之前设置 `state.keyed.max-parallelism`，并保持其稳定："

msgid ""
"The Dashboard and stable state API require job snapshot publication "
"through `observability.dashboard.enabled`, which is enabled by default."
msgstr "Dashboard 和稳定状态 API 要求通过 `observability.dashboard.enabled` 发布作业快照；该选项默认启用。"

msgid ""
"Use stable, unique operator names when constructing the graph. The "
"Dashboard shows numeric operator IDs, current parallelism, and a runtime-"
"provided reason when an operator cannot be resized."
msgstr "构造图时，请使用稳定且唯一的算子名称。Dashboard 会显示数字算子 ID、当前并行度；无法调整算子时，还会显示运行时提供的原因。"

msgid ""
"Operator chaining is enabled by default. Compatible stateless operators "
"on a forward edge can become one physical operator, including a chain "
"rooted at a source that cannot be resized. Treat the published operator "
"snapshot as the authoritative set of scaling units. Set `pipeline"
".operator-chaining.enabled=false` before submission when a transform must"
" remain independently rescalable."
msgstr ""
"算子链默认启用。forward "
"边上兼容的无状态算子可以合并为一个物理算子，其中也可能包括以不可调整源为根的链。请将已发布的算子快照视为扩缩容单元的权威集合。如果某个转换必须保持可独立扩缩容，请在提交前设置"
" `pipeline.operator-chaining.enabled=false`。"

msgid "Resize an operator"
msgstr "调整算子并行度"

msgid ""
"Start the bundled Dashboard from a machine that can connect to the Ray "
"cluster:"
msgstr "在能够连接 Ray 集群的机器上启动随附的 Dashboard："

msgid ""
"Select a running job, enter the target parallelism on an enabled "
"operator, and apply the change. The server returns as soon as the "
"JobManager accepts the operation. You can close the operator panel, "
"navigate away, or close the page; the JobManager continues the rescale. "
"The execution graph and operator table are driven by the polled job "
"snapshot, so reopening the page reconstructs the current target and phase"
" instead of relying on browser-local state."
msgstr ""
"选择一个运行中的作业，在可调整的算子上输入目标并行度并应用变更。服务器会在 JobManager 接受操作后立即返回。你可以关闭算子面板、切换页面或关闭浏览器页面；JobManager "
"仍会继续扩缩容。执行图和算子表由轮询得到的作业快照驱动，因此重新打开页面时会根据快照重建当前目标和阶段，而不依赖浏览器本地状态。"

msgid "The Dashboard shows these operation states:"
msgstr "Dashboard 会显示以下操作状态："

msgid "Status"
msgstr "状态"

msgid "Dashboard meaning"
msgstr "Dashboard 含义"

msgid "`ACCEPTED`"
msgstr "`ACCEPTED`"

msgid "The operation is queued by the JobManager."
msgstr "操作已进入 JobManager 队列。"

msgid "`RUNNING`"
msgstr "`RUNNING`"

msgid "Task instances and routes are being coordinated."
msgstr "正在协调任务实例和路由。"

msgid "`STABILIZING`"
msgstr "`STABILIZING`"

msgid ""
"The new parallelism is committed and its stabilization checkpoint is "
"pending."
msgstr "新并行度已提交，正在等待稳定化检查点。"

msgid "`COMPLETED`"
msgstr "`COMPLETED`"

msgid "The topology and stabilization checkpoint are complete."
msgstr "拓扑变更和稳定化检查点均已完成。"

msgid "`NOOP`"
msgstr "`NOOP`"

msgid "The requested parallelism already matched the operator."
msgstr "请求的并行度已与算子当前并行度一致。"

msgid "`REJECTED`"
msgstr "`REJECTED`"

msgid "A precondition or request was invalid."
msgstr "前置条件或请求无效。"

msgid "`FAILED`"
msgstr "`FAILED`"

msgid ""
"The runtime operation failed; the snapshot reports the retained topology "
"and error."
msgstr "运行时操作失败；快照会报告保留的拓扑和错误。"

msgid ""
"The latest per-operator record is available as "
"`operator[\"rescale_operation\"]`; recent job-level records are available"
" as `job[\"rescale_operations\"]`. Both remain observable across page "
"refreshes. Only one operation can run at a time, and the runtime keeps "
"later rescale controls disabled through `STABILIZING`."
msgstr ""
"最新的算子级记录位于 `operator[\"rescale_operation\"]`；近期的作业级记录位于 "
"`job[\"rescale_operations\"]`。刷新页面后两者仍可观测。一次只能运行一个操作，运行时会在整个 `STABILIZING` 阶段禁用后续扩缩容控件。"

msgid ""
"See [Observe Klein jobs](observability.md) before exposing the Dashboard "
"beyond its loopback listener."
msgstr "将 Dashboard 暴露到回环监听地址之外前，请参阅[观测 Klein 作业](observability.md)。"

msgid ""
"Automation that needs to wait for the topology result can use the stable,"
" synchronous state API:"
msgstr "需要等待拓扑结果的自动化程序可以使用稳定的同步状态 API："

msgid "The result is JSON-safe and has one of these statuses:"
msgstr "结果可以安全地序列化为 JSON，并具有以下状态之一："

msgid "Meaning"
msgstr "含义"

msgid "Next action"
msgstr "后续操作"

msgid "The topology change committed."
msgstr "拓扑变更已提交。"

msgid "Wait for the stabilization checkpoint, then validate rates and lag."
msgstr "等待稳定化检查点完成，然后验证速率和延迟。"

msgid "The target already has that parallelism."
msgstr "目标已经具有该并行度。"

msgid "No action is required."
msgstr "无需操作。"

msgid "Read `error` and correct the request."
msgstr "读取 `error` 并修正请求。"

msgid "The runtime operation raised an error."
msgstr "运行时操作引发错误。"

msgid "Refresh the job snapshot before deciding whether to retry."
msgstr "决定是否重试前，请刷新作业快照。"

msgid ""
"A result of `None` means that the job is no longer published in this "
"cluster. A client timeout only stops that caller from waiting. The remote"
" operation can still commit. Likewise, a `FAILED` response can follow the"
" topology commit if a later checkpoint-gate response fails. Never retry "
"blindly; first refresh `get_job_snapshot()` and compare the operator's "
"current parallelism."
msgstr ""
"结果为 `None` "
"表示该作业已不再发布到此集群。客户端超时只会让该调用方停止等待，远程操作仍可能提交。同样，如果后续检查点门控响应失败，也可能在拓扑提交后收到 "
"`FAILED` 响应。切勿盲目重试；请先刷新 `get_job_snapshot()`，并比较算子的当前并行度。"

msgid "What happens at the local cut?"
msgstr "局部切点处会发生什么？"

msgid ""
"On scale-out, Klein creates and pings only the added actors. Subtasks "
"whose indexes exist at both parallelisms retain their Ray actor "
"identities."
msgstr "扩容时，Klein 只创建并探测新增 actor。在新旧并行度中索引均存在的子任务会保留其 Ray actor 身份。"

msgid ""
"The coordinator pauses new checkpoints and waits for in-flight checkpoint"
" completion before changing the data plane."
msgstr "协调器暂停创建新检查点，并等待在途检查点完成后再更改数据平面。"

msgid ""
"Direct upstream tasks insert an ordered local barrier and pause at that "
"cut. A directly connected source pauses cooperatively at a record "
"boundary; unrelated regions keep running."
msgstr "直接上游任务会插入一个有序局部屏障，并在该切点暂停。直接连接的源会在记录边界协同暂停；不相关区域继续运行。"

msgid ""
"The target aligns the barriers, snapshots managed state, and fences its "
"direct downstream tasks. Retained and added actors prepare the new "
"runtime and their assigned state while the old runtime remains available."
msgstr "目标对齐屏障、生成托管状态快照，并为其直接下游任务设置围栏。在旧运行时仍可用期间，保留和新增的 actor 会准备新运行时及各自分配的状态。"

msgid ""
"Klein commits the new topology and routing atomically. A pre-commit "
"failure rolls back to the old runtime. On scale-in, only surplus actors "
"are stopped after commit."
msgstr "Klein 以原子方式提交新拓扑和路由。提交前故障会回滚到旧运行时。缩容时，只有多余 actor 会在提交后停止。"

msgid ""
"The source emits an ordinary stabilization checkpoint. Until it becomes "
"durable, a task failure deliberately escalates to consistent global "
"checkpoint recovery instead of restoring one task from stale state."
msgstr "源会发出一个普通的稳定化检查点。在其持久化之前，任务故障会有意升级为一致的全局检查点恢复，而不是从陈旧状态恢复单个任务。"

msgid ""
"Keyed state moves by stable key group; keys are not rehashed with "
"Python's process-local `hash()`. The operation does not change connector "
"delivery guarantees, so sinks still need the idempotency or transaction "
"design described in [Delivery semantics](delivery-semantics.md)."
msgstr ""
"键控状态按稳定键组移动；键不会使用 Python 的进程本地 `hash()` 重新哈希。该操作不会改变连接器交付保证，因此 sink "
"仍需要[交付语义](delivery-semantics.md)中所述的幂等或事务设计。"

msgid ""
"An incident `FORWARD` edge is valid only while its endpoints have equal "
"parallelism. Klein changes that edge to its normal shuffle choice when a "
"rescale makes the counts differ. Explicit non-forward partitioners are "
"preserved."
msgstr ""
"相连的 `FORWARD` 边仅在两端并行度相等时有效。扩缩容导致数量不同时，Klein 会将该边改为其常规 shuffle 选择。显式非 "
"forward 分区器会被保留。"

msgid "Coordinate with Ray cluster autoscaling"
msgstr "与 Ray 集群自动伸缩协调"

msgid ""
"Ray's cluster autoscaler is outside Klein. A streaming scale-out creates "
"actor CPU/GPU demands that an already configured cluster autoscaler can "
"satisfy, but node provisioning must finish within "
"`job.scheduler.start.timeout`. The operator request can otherwise time "
"out while waiting for its added actors."
msgstr ""
"Ray 集群自动伸缩器位于 Klein 之外。流式扩容会产生 actor CPU/GPU "
"需求，已配置的集群自动伸缩器可满足这些需求，但节点供应必须在 `job.scheduler.start.timeout` "
"内完成，否则算子请求可能在等待新增 actor 时超时。"

msgid ""
"Existing job-wide PlacementGroup bundles are not resized. Added scale-out"
" actors use Ray's native placement, and bundles made surplus by scale-in "
"remain reserved until the job ends. A streaming scale-in therefore does "
"not guarantee that the cluster autoscaler can remove a node."
msgstr ""
"现有作业级 PlacementGroup bundle 不会调整大小。扩容新增的 actor 使用 Ray 原生放置；缩容后多余的 bundle "
"仍会保留到作业结束。因此，流式缩容并不保证集群自动伸缩器能够移除节点。"

msgid "Validate and automate safely"
msgstr "安全地验证和自动化"

msgid "After a completed request, verify that:"
msgstr "请求完成后，请验证："

msgid ""
"the operator snapshot reports the target `parallelism` and all instances "
"are running;"
msgstr "算子快照报告目标 `parallelism`，且所有实例都在运行；"

msgid ""
"`job[\"checkpoints\"][\"rescale_recovery_fenced\"]` becomes `False` after"
" a new completed checkpoint;"
msgstr "新检查点完成后，`job[\"checkpoints\"][\"rescale_recovery_fenced\"]` 变为 `False`；"

msgid ""
"source lag, throughput, busy time, and backpressure move in the expected "
"direction; and"
msgstr "源延迟、吞吐量、忙碌时间和背压按预期方向变化；"

msgid ""
"checkpoint duration, external connections, and sink fan-out remain within"
" their operating limits."
msgstr "检查点持续时间、外部连接和 sink 扇出保持在运行限制以内。"

msgid ""
"An external autoscaling controller should use both interval averages and "
"the hottest-subtask values, require several consecutive samples, apply "
"hysteresis and a cooldown, and enforce explicit minimum and maximum "
"parallelism. It should submit a request only while `can_rescale` is true,"
" serialize changes, and wait for the recovery fence to clear. "
"Backpressure alone is not sufficient: a slow sink, broker limit, or hot "
"key can get worse when parallelism increases."
msgstr ""
"外部自动伸缩控制器应同时使用区间平均值和最热子任务值，要求连续多次采样，应用迟滞和冷却机制，并强制设置显式的最小与最大并行度。它只应在 "
"`can_rescale` 为 true 时提交请求，串行化变更，并等待恢复围栏清除。仅凭背压不足以决策：慢速 sink、broker "
"限制或热点键可能会在并行度增加后进一步恶化。"

msgid ""
"For symptom-oriented tuning, see [Tune Klein performance](performance-"
"tuning.md). For changing parallelism while resubmitting from a durable "
"checkpoint, see [Restore and rescale a job](checkpoint-recovery.md)."
msgstr ""
"有关面向症状的调优，请参阅[调优 Klein 性能](performance-"
"tuning.md)。有关从持久检查点重新提交时调整并行度，请参阅[恢复作业并调整其并行度](checkpoint-recovery.md)。"

#~ msgid "Automation can use the same stable state API:"
#~ msgstr "自动化程序可以使用相同的稳定状态 API："
